==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Celtiberian
<hw>Celt`i*be"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>Celtiber</ets>, <ets>Celtibericus</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or
pertaining to the ancient Celtiberia (a district in Spain lying between
the Ebro and the Tagus) or its inhabitants the Celtiberi (Celts of the
river Iberus).</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>An inhabitant of
Celtiberia.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Celtic</ent>⟦br⟧
